policy.Description: Grants full access to AWS Migration Hub Refactor Spaces and other AWS related services except AWS Transit Gateway and EC2 security groups not required when using environments without a network bridge. This policy also excludes permissions required for AWS Lambda and AWS Resource Access Manager as they can be scoped down based on tags.

Grants full access to AWS MigrationHub Refactor Spaces, AWS MigrationHub Refactor Spaces console features and other related AWS services except permissions required for AWS Lambda and AWS Resource Access Manager as they can be scoped down based on tags.
Provides read-only access to AWS services and resources.
